 \sqrt{D} = \mathrm{diag} (\sqrt{\lambda_1}, \sqrt{\lambda_2}, \dots , \sqrt{\lambda_n} ) \ , 
 \left( S^t \sqrt{D} S   \right)^2 = \left( S^t \sqrt{D} S\right) \left(S^t \sqrt{D} S \right) = S^t \left( \sqrt{D}\right)^2 S = S^t D S = A \ . 
